|                                                                              |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


[002] Usage 
________________________________________________________________________________

Refer to the manual pages and the ":help" in the software.


[003] Optional dependency
________________________________________________________________________________

If luajit is installed on the system's user, lua scripts can be used by the 
user to extend the functionalities of sc-im. 

